#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calories_burned_calculator.html:422
msgid ""
"Compares calories burned across different activities for the same duration "
"and weight. This helps you choose activities that match your calorie-burning "
"goals."
