"Fat helps with satiety and nutrient absorption. Include healthy fats in each "
"meal for better satisfaction and vitamin absorption."
msgstr ""

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:487
msgid ""
"Individual fat needs vary based on activity level, metabolism, body "
"composition goals, and personal preferences."
