msgstr ""

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:361
msgid ""
"Higher weight gain is recommended to support healthy fetal development and "
"maternal health. Focus on nutrient-dense foods and regular meals."
msgstr ""

