#, python-format
msgid ""
"Dew point is the temperature at which air becomes saturated with water vapor "
"and condensation begins to form. It is a measure of atmospheric moisture. "
"When the air temperature drops to the dew point, relative humidity reaches "
"100%%, and water vapor condenses into liquid water (dew). The dew point is "
"always less than or equal to the air temperature."
